        <updateDate>2008-01-04T15:01:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Health Insurance Tax Credit Assistance Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a tax credit for charitable contributions to tax-exempt charities which subsidize health insurance premiums and pharmacy co-payments of uninsured individuals or individuals who cannot otherwise afford health insurance or drug treatments.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
